                    <h3 style="font-size:22px; font-weight:bold; text-align:center; color:#ff6600;">How are we different?</h3> With conventional credit reports only painting part of the picture, ICSM operate a unique Members Only Electronic Credit Community\Credit abuse network, on line computerized blacklist. Our members exchange information regarding their customers, whose accounts are on stop, bouncing cheques, under threat of legal action, etc. for non-payment of invoices. We call our unique information a Datascan. </div>
